<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login ‚ÄĒ WA-RS</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=Outfit:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        :root {
            --bg-void: #0a0a0f;
            --bg-surface: #12121a;
            --bg-elevated: #1a1a24;
            --bg-hover: #22222e;
            --border-dim: #2a2a3a;
            --border-glow: #3a3a4a;
            --text-primary: #e8e8f0;
            --text-secondary: #8888a0;
            --text-dim: #555566;
            --accent-primary: #00ff9d;
            --accent-secondary: #00cc7d;
            --accent-glow: rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.15);
            --danger: #ff4757;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg-void);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 0%, rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 100%, rgba(0, 100, 255, 0.02) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }

        .login-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 440px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .terminal-window {
            background: var(--bg-surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .terminal-header {
            background: var(--bg-elevated);
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
        }

        .terminal-dot {
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .terminal-dot.red { background: #ff5f56; }
        .terminal-dot.yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
        .terminal-dot.green { background: #27ca40; }

        .terminal-title {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-right: 44px;
        }

        .terminal-body {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .ascii-logo {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.45rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);
        }

        .prompt {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .prompt-line {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .prompt-symbol {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .prompt-path {
            color: #6c99bb;
        }

        .prompt-text {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .form-label {
            display: block;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .form-label::before {
            content: '$ ';
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .input-wrapper {
            position: relative;
        }

        .form-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            background: var(--bg-void);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-dim);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .form-input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent-primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-glow), 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);
        }

        .form-input::placeholder {
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            color: #000;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: var(--accent-secondary);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px var(--accent-glow);
        }

        .btn-primary::before {
            content: '>';
        }

        .alert {
            padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .alert-danger {
            background: rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.3);
            color: var(--danger);
        }

        .alert-danger::before {
            content: '[ERROR]';
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .hint {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
        }

        .hint code {
            background: var(--bg-elevated);
            padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .cursor {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 16px;
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            animation: blink 1s step-end infinite;
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin-left: 2px;
        }

        @keyframes blink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0; }
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="terminal-window">
            <div class="terminal-header">
                <div class="terminal-dot red"></div>
                <div class="terminal-dot yellow"></div>
                <div class="terminal-dot green"></div>
                <div class="terminal-title">wa-rs ‚ÄĒ login</div>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal-body">
                <pre class="ascii-logo">‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó    ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó       ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó
‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ    ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó      ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ
‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ ‚Ėą‚ēó ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēĚ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó
‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēó‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ
‚ēö‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĒ‚ēĚ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ      ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ  ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚Ėą‚ēĎ
 ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ  ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ      ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ  ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēĚ‚ēö‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēĚ</pre>

                <div class="prompt">
                    <div class="prompt-line">
                        <span class="prompt-symbol">‚ěú</span>
                        <span class="prompt-path">~/wa-rs</span>
                        <span class="prompt-text">authenticate<span class="cursor"></span></span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                {% match error %}
                {% when Some with (err) %}
                <div class="alert alert-danger">{{ err }}</div>
                {% when None %}
                {% endmatch %}

                <form method="POST" action="/dashboard/login">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label class="form-label">enter_token</label>
                        <div class="input-wrapper">
                            <input type="password" name="token" class="form-input" placeholder="eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..." required autofocus>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">authenticate</button>
                </form>

                <p class="hint">
                    Token from logs or <code>SUPERADMIN_TOKEN</code>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="https://github.com/fdciabdul/wa-rs" target="_blank">github</a>
            <a href="https://wa-rs.imtaqin.id/" target="_blank">docs</a>
            <a href="/swagger-ui" target="_blank">api</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
